comment: Johnny depp is the ultimate Grindelwald
commentable_entity.ask: Remake Secrets of Dumbledore with the true Gellert Grindelwald
commentable_entity.title: Remake Secrets of Dumbledore with the true Gellert Grindelwald
commentable_entity.description: Johnny Depp was wrongly removed from this film franchise over false accusations made by his former wife Amber Heard. Many of us both fan's of Johnny Depp films or fans of the Harry Potter/ Fantastic Beast movie were shocked after he was released from the movie without being found guilt of any accusations made my Amber Heard. While Johnny Depp lost everything he's worked for Amber Heard was still casted in Aquaman 2 and was allowed to start filming. The point of this is to help Johnny Depp reclaim one of his many beloved and rightful characters. So please sign this so we can truly start having justice for Johnny Depp.
